Subject: Re: [T2] could it be the coil?

Hi Mike,

The fact that you had to turn the switch to get power to the coil tells me
it's your ignition switch. It's either loose, or it's malfunctioning.

Try re-seating it at the connection at the base of the ignition lock
cylinder, that might get it back in order.

Happy Trails,

